title: Taper's Section - Grateful Dead - 192 kbps MP3 - 8.58 GB
description:
Taper&#039;s Section - Selections from the vault streamed at www.dead.net

Weeks 1-38 - November 27, 2006 - August 19, 2007

This feature allowed downloading for the first 38 weeks, after that it was 

streaming only. This collection consists of all the tracks from those first 38 

weeks. 396 tracks, all 192 kbps MP3 as they were released from the vault by 

David Lemieux. Tracks are arranged into "discs", one "disc" for each week&#039;s songs.
